    <bodyTop>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Emma is one of only two students who beat off stiff competition to win the place based at the four star Macdonald Cardrona Hotel, Golf &amp; Spa by Peebles.</p>
<p>Emma, a 2nd year undergraduate (BA Honours in Hospitality and Tourism Management) at Queen Margaret University, is now on a nine month placement at the 99 bedroom hotel. Emma is part of an innovative scheme developed by the group. </p>
<p>Emma commented: “I am so proud to be part of the Macdonald family at Macdonald Cardrona Hotel Golf &amp; Spa.  I’m learning a great deal from experienced colleagues who give me invaluable insights into Macdonald Hotels’ commitment to ensure guests enjoy a warm welcome and friendly professional service.  As part of the hotel operations family, I’m also learning about the group’s commitment to always serve diners the finest freshest produce. </p>
<p>“There’s a lot to learn and I’d love to return here one day in a senior role.  This undergraduate scheme is certainly giving me all the tools to achieve that goal.”</p>]]></Value>
